[
    {
        "text": "However, it's not all doom and gloom.",
        "startTime": 3195,
        "endTime": 5823,
        "slowStartTime": 4943,
        "slowEndTime": 8959
    },
    {
        "text": "In 1987, over 30 countries signed the Montreal Protocol,...",
        "startTime": 6593,
        "endTime": 11184,
        "slowStartTime": 10040,
        "slowEndTime": 17001
    },
    {
        "text": "...in which the signatories agreed to cut CFC use by 50 percent by the year 2000.",
        "startTime": 11628,
        "endTime": 17569,
        "slowStartTime": 17592,
        "slowEndTime": 26578
    },
    {
        "text": "This protocol was further extended two years later,...",
        "startTime": 18617,
        "endTime": 21614,
        "slowStartTime": 28076,
        "slowEndTime": 32646
    },
    {
        "text": "...when over 80 countries agreed to stop using CFCs completely by the year 2000.",
        "startTime": 22079,
        "endTime": 27418,
        "slowStartTime": 33268,
        "slowEndTime": 41352
    },
    {
        "text": "Also, in 1991, a fund was set up to help developing countries...",
        "startTime": 28657,
        "endTime": 33664,
        "slowStartTime": 43135,
        "slowEndTime": 50721
    },
    {
        "text": "...change over to non-CFC technologies, and it has met with some success.",
        "startTime": 33784,
        "endTime": 38832,
        "slowStartTime": 50826,
        "slowEndTime": 58473
    },
    {
        "text": "Hopefully, new technologies will continue to provide safer alternatives...",
        "startTime": 39729,
        "endTime": 43672,
        "slowStartTime": 59744,
        "slowEndTime": 65733
    },
    {
        "text": "...to CFCs, HCFCs and other gases that harm the atmosphere.",
        "startTime": 43815,
        "endTime": 49049,
        "slowStartTime": 65873,
        "slowEndTime": 73799
    },
    {
        "text": "One current example is the increase in use of coolants in air conditioning units...",
        "startTime": 50318,
        "endTime": 54745,
        "slowStartTime": 75627,
        "slowEndTime": 82342
    },
    {
        "text": "...which break down into relatively harmless compounds...",
        "startTime": 54834,
        "endTime": 57548,
        "slowStartTime": 82401,
        "slowEndTime": 86547
    },
    {
        "text": "...before they can reach the stratosphere.",
        "startTime": 57637,
        "endTime": 59498,
        "slowStartTime": 86606,
        "slowEndTime": 89472
    },
    {
        "text": "However, there is still some use of ozone-depleting gases...",
        "startTime": 60859,
        "endTime": 64529,
        "slowStartTime": 91438,
        "slowEndTime": 97018
    },
    {
        "text": "...such as methyl bromide in some pesticides,...",
        "startTime": 64957,
        "endTime": 67849,
        "slowStartTime": 97585,
        "slowEndTime": 101998
    },
    {
        "text": "...and some countries who haven't signed the Montreal Protocol are still using CFCs.",
        "startTime": 68372,
        "endTime": 73292,
        "slowStartTime": 102708,
        "slowEndTime": 110163
    },
    {
        "text": "Because of this, and because of the long lifespan of the CFCs...",
        "startTime": 74282,
        "endTime": 78207,
        "slowStartTime": 111573,
        "slowEndTime": 117536
    },
    {
        "text": "...that are already in the stratosphere,...",
        "startTime": 78301,
        "endTime": 80064,
        "slowStartTime": 117602,
        "slowEndTime": 120321
    },
    {
        "text": "...it's estimated that it will take several lifetimes for the ozone layer to recover.",
        "startTime": 80643,
        "endTime": 85077,
        "slowStartTime": 121114,
        "slowEndTime": 127840
    }
]